[38.591199, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36mACT 2 — THE REVEAL   (~30 sec)   The kicker.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[38.591579, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Everything you just watched came from typing this in front of my”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “training command. No config. No instrumentation. No pipeline file.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;37m  $ roar run python train.py\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[41.606223, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “That's it. That's the whole integration. It was free.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[41.606641, "o", "\r\n"]
[44.619518, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Free, but not fooled. Watch what happens if the tree is dirty.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[44.620011, "o", "\u001b[1;32m$ touch test.txt\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[44.633126, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ roar run python evaluate.py\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[44.929029, "o", "Error: Run blocked: working tree is dirty.\r\n\r\nCode changes:\r\n  cast/demo.cast\r\n\r\nFix:\r\n  git add cast/demo.cast\r\n  git commit -m \"<describe your changes>\"\r\n\r\nOther untracked files:\r\n  test.txt\r\n\r\nFix — gitignore or commit:\r\n  echo 'test.txt' >> .gitignore\r\n  git add .gitignore && git commit -m 'ignore outputs'\r\n  (or `git add test.txt` + commit)\r\n\r\nThen retry: roar run python evaluate.py\r\n\r\nWhy: https://glaas.ai/docs/why-clean-commits\r\n"]
[44.943487, "o", "\r\n"]
[47.949631, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “It won't record a run it can't pin to exact code. Everything passes”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “through the commit — that's the bottleneck. Which is why the record you're”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[47.949916, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “about to see is complete enough to catch what I never declared.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[50.95911, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36mACT 3 — PAYOFF   (~2 min)   The record surfaces what I never declared.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[50.959454, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “One human act. I marked the raw dataset as containing personal data.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ roar tag show data/raw.csv\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[51.302028, "o", "Tags on data/raw.csv:\r\n  contains_pii=present\r\n"]
[51.328808, "o", "\r\n"]
[54.337865, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “I never said anything about the other files. Watch where it went.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ python taint.py\u001b[0m\r\n"]
