[60.802103, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Five artifacts. One declaration. The tag followed the data, not a config.”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “That's a blast radius — and it's the answer to 'which models are affected?'”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[60.802349, "o", "\r\n"]
[63.813491, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “And it's not a guess. Ask the model why it's tainted, and it shows its work.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ roar tag why contains_pii model.pkl\u001b[0m\r\n"]
